                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for visually and quantitatively detecting lead ions in flavors and fragrances by using ratio fluorescent probe",
                    "一种比率荧光探针可视化定量检测香精香料中铅离子的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The method comprises the following steps: mixing glutathione and a hydrogen peroxide aqueous solution, transferring the mixture into a reaction container for reaction to prepare a blue carbon dot solution, mixing the blue carbon dot solution with a rhodamine B dye solution, diluting the mixture with a BR buffer solution, and detecting the lead ions in the flavors and fragrances. The ratio fluorescent probe solution can be used for detecting the lead ion-containing solution. The method is simple in pretreatment, easy and convenient to operate, good in repeatability, high in sensitivity, low in detection limit and good in precision, the content of the lead ions in essence and fragrance samples can be rapidly, visually and quantitatively detected, the limitation of large instruments in a laboratory can be eliminated by combining a smart phone, and rapid, visual and quantitative analysis of the lead ions on site is achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种比率荧光探针可视化定量检测香精香料中铅离子的方法，包括以下步骤：将谷胱甘肽和过氧化氢水溶液混合后转移至反应容器中反应，制备得到蓝色碳点溶液，并与罗丹明B染料溶液混合，通过BR缓冲溶液稀释，得到比率荧光探针溶液，即可对含铅离子溶液检测。本发明前处理简单、操作简便、重复性好、灵敏度高、检测限低、精密度好，能够快速可视化定量检测香精香料样品中铅离子含量，结合智能手机可摆脱实验室大型仪器限制，实现对铅离子现场快速可视化定量分析。"
                }
            ]
        }
